body_html: The specialized op for tf.parse_single_example() was added in 96f3023, which is not part of TensorFlow 1.5.0. It sounds like the mobilenet module that you're trying to freeze was generated by a later version of TensorFlow. To use that op or freeze a graph using it, you will need to upgrade to TF 1.6.0rc0 or later.
